                <div class="rendering rendering_researchoutput  rendering_researchoutput_apa rendering_contributiontobookanthology rendering_apa rendering_contributiontobookanthology_apa">Callahan, A.<a rel="Person" href="https://cris.maastrichtuniversity.nl/en/persons/michel-dumontier/" class="link"><span>, &amp; Dumontier, M.</span></a> (2012). <a rel="ContributionToBookAnthology" href="https://cris.maastrichtuniversity.nl/en/publications/evaluating-scientific-hypotheses-using-the-sparql-inferencing-not/" class="link"><span>Evaluating scientific hypotheses using the SPARQL inferencing notation</span></a>. In <em>The Semantic Web: Research and Applications: 9th Extended Semantic Web Conference, ESWC 2012, Heraklion, Crete, Greece, May 27-31, 2012. Proceedings </em>(pp. 647-658). Springer. <a onclick="window.open(this.href, '_blank','noopener,noreferrer'); return false;" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-642-30284-8_50" class="link"><span>https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-642-30284-8_50</span></a></div>
